{"tid":781424,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人做任何事都係半桶水？","createTime":"2018-08-16T01:30:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T02:27:20.000Z","uid":189695,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c69e275cb4562d41014ec59fddc423ef698fee86","tid":781424,"uid":189695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:30:21.000Z","msg":"有冇人做任何事都係半桶水？<br />\n<br />\n玩樂器，籃球，足球，讀書。 <br />\n<br />\n全部得半桶水，唔係最廢個批，比平均高小小，但又唔係最top個批。<br />\n<br />\n好似乜都識小小，但就冇樣叻。<br />\n<br />\n好想有一樣野可以係做到最top<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da78395fbcf5466d535115bf58dd038acafa8160","tid":781424,"uid":162316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:35:01.000Z","msg":"有 每次有少少成就就會hea落黎<br />\n唔知係覺得登頂太難定安於現狀<br />\n跟住就會好快比人超越"},{"pid":"af2f7c7916a958651256eb0d37189851048773bd","tid":781424,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:52:22.000Z","msg":"三分鐘熱度後就會半桶水<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e0ff4c36ec19a7b0109c75fe17a9e877fa14c16","tid":781424,"uid":7458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:54:04.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過小提琴 結他 鋼琴 畫畫 芭蕾舞 冇樣學得成<br />\n唯一有樣野叻就係打機 由細到大都keep住玩 不過打機對我黎講唔算係專長<br />\n呢排想學黑白相上色 睇下幾耐之後會放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"343106a4bd72e8590d26e5b7c947f271d332324a","tid":781424,"uid":100230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T02:15:43.000Z","msg":"周身刀 冇張利"},{"pid":"562f1800977725a28a41c1475f806aee742dd52d","tid":781424,"uid":34461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T02:16:04.000Z","msg":"有天材 為何我們"},{"pid":"38e854174c13a224d7c290836483d773ef359600","tid":781424,"uid":34461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T02:23:26.000Z","msg":"其實呢個世界有幾種人<br />\n1.蠢人廢人<br />\n咩都學極唔識，周身都無刀，唔好話利<br />\n2.正常人<br />\n學嘢都算快上手，但去到樽頸位除咗勤力之外，其實都真係要好叻先突破到，最後形成大家見到嘅周身刀無張利<br />\n3.叻過正常人少少<br />\n有啲係叻有啲係好勤力，總有一樣嘢係突破到，叫做有一樣嘢係成功<br />\n4.超勁超勤力嘅人<br />\n天時地利人和，自己有料又有資源又肯去勤力，周身刀張張利<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以樓主，其實我哋都係平凡人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0995f68a929cb484ca2888b3340790f9ffe4bfeb","tid":781424,"uid":82482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T02:27:20.000Z","msg":"10000小時定律"}]}